title: Spacious, 2 Bedroom With Pool, Marina Views, Pet Friendly!
posting_body: ['Live Coastal Cool', 'Welcome to the new MDR', 'A beautiful and bright space that provides a sense of coastal luxury, Neptune Marina offers the surf at your door and the city at your fingertips.', 'Rooted in the culture that has defined the Marina for generations, the breezy seaside aesthetic joins Mid-Century Modern elements with an emotional interpretation of the physical landscape.', 'Neptune Marina is an aspirational community by the water.', 'This seaside oasis caters to affluent achievers and tech connoisseurs who are seeking quality of life in the perfect Los Angeles sanctuary.', 'Our touring schedules and operating hours may vary as we continue to follow local phased opening guidelines and direction from local health officials.', 'Please visit our community website for up to date information.', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 88', 'OR Text', '88', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to contact our team.', 'Use this link for more info:', '<URL>', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1335 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Front Loading Washers & Dryers', '- Modern Wide-Plank Flooring', '- Custom Designed Interior Finishes', '- Kitchen Islands with Wine Chillers (select residences)', '- Full Suite of Stainless Steel Appliances with Gas Cooking', '- Designer Cabinets', '- Quartz Countertops and Backsplashes (select residences)', 'Community Amenities', '- State-of-the-Art Fitness Centers with Yoga Studio', "- Skydecks with Outdoor Chef's Kitchens, Lounge Seating & TVs", '- Business Center with Private Conference Room', '- 24-Hr Package Retrieval System', '- Resort Inspired Heated Pool & Spa', '- Pet-Friendly', '- Clubrooms with Kitchen, Gaming & TVs', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Sunday:10:00AM-6:00PM', 'Neptune Marina', '14126 Marquesas Way, Marina Del Rey, CA, 90292', 'Greystar California, Inc., Broker License #01525765', 'DMCA Agent: <URL>', '0S18urOvW']
